body:
installing Flutter plugin v45 in android studio 192.7142 makes it totally frozen for about 20 seconds when switching editor dart tabs,
switching back Flutter plugin to v44 solved the problem.

comment_data.body: I can't reproduce this. Does it happen it you switch back to M45? If so, is there any other indicator of what's happening? Maybe a message in the bottom status bar, a notification balloon, or anything else changing in the UI?
